{"tid":1276162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我係港共政權，我第一個會想搞連仔","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T01:59:36.000Z","uid":226471,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb053c0c64dbe56a146ba71b230cb916bba9f5f","tid":1276162,"uid":226471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"由佢決定抽起廣告方便資訊流通、解鎖有用po 1001、推最新即時消息比巴絲，到後黎開P牌制度 del email，全部都係積極參與緊呢場運動嘅大backup。<br />\n我係港共政權的話一定會整個莫須有嘅罪名比連仔，成場運動肯定事倍功半。<br />\n我每一日都好驚睇到新聞話「某大型討論區管理員被捕」，所以真係請連仔注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n真係好多謝連仔為香港嘅付出。"},{"pid":"fa46fd2937e83747be528138b6343c672dd3c74f","tid":1276162,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"連仔唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c949935c0f75bce4429e27df5f27e062b96ecec6","tid":1276162,"uid":226471,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"真係驚<br />\n難得有一個真係幫緊我地嘅admin<br />\n你睇隔離登"},{"pid":"e5ff7259a1f015d2f6855c2a751a49ef4b1399a8","tid":1276162,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45d85fd9109912e6a47ff43c96259e468c73d399","tid":1276162,"uid":98726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"多謝連仔"},{"pid":"31274011bd3ed71b483a77cd465c024d9a9a28d8","tid":1276162,"uid":226471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"其實我地有冇野可以幫到保護連仔?"},{"pid":"93f7f0f3e3009cd2064efb9f7ab5f93bea7fbf2e","tid":1276162,"uid":13467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:59:36.000Z","msg":"希望連仔會頂得順<br />\n利申已課金"}]}